data.text: @DavidRutley @AstraZeneca @UniofOxford Pity that it isn’t going to be administered according to the schedule used in the trials

@marymarkg @DavidRutley @AstraZeneca @UniofOxford Agreed. 60 4/5 year olds in our 2 Reception classes with free flow so as much as we’re doing our best to keep our hands, faces and spaces, a vaccine would be reassuring.

@DavidRutley @AstraZeneca @UniofOxford Brilliant!.......Now we need to vaccinate teachers as a priority. No teacher should be expected to be in a room with a class of children all day (25, 6 year olds in my case) without being vaccinated. Keep education and the economy going - VACCINATE TEACHERS NOW!
